original: Zetterqvist, Sven Robert Ferdinand, disponent, Åmål, f. 3/2/94 i Uddevalla av J. A. Z. o. Ehsabetih Hult. G. m. Emy Elvira Larsson, d. 41. Barn: Stig, Birgitta (Britta), Tore. — Stud. v. Uddevalla h. a. 1. samt merk. stud. Res. t. Norge, Danm., Finl., Tyskl., Tjeckoslov. o. Österr. Anst. v. ol. föret. 12-15, kamr. v. A-B Sv. Elektromagne-ter i Åmål 16-24, inköpte o. ombild. det 24. Verkst. dir. där sed. 24. Styr:led. i fl. boL, led. av styr. f. Sv. Hand :bank. avd:kont. i Åmål, led. av folksk:styr.
translated: Zetterqvist, Sven Robert Ferdinand, manager, Åmål, b. 3/2/94 in Uddevalla to J. A. Z. and Ehsabetih Hult. Married to Emy Elvira Larsson, deceased in 1941. Children: Stig, Birgitta (Britta), Tore. — Stud. at Uddevalla high school 1st year and further studies. Traveled to Norway, Denmark, Finland, Germany, Czechoslovakia, and Austria to study. Employed at various companies from 1912 to 1915. Employed as a chamberlain at A-B Sv. Elektromagneter in Åmål from 1916 to 1924, bought and restructured the company in 1924. Appointed as the director since then. Board member in several companies, member of the board for the Swedish Handbank department office in Åmål, member of the school board.
